Nationwide Building Society said it isissuing 30 mln stg of index-linked loan stock due 2021 by wayof a placing on a yield basis in the domestic sterling market.    The issue's real rate of return, price and the amount ofthe first interest payment will be fixed at 1400 gmt today. Thereal rate of return will be the sum of 0.60 pct plus the grossreal rate of return on the 2-1/2 pct index-linked Treasurystock due 2020.    The issue will be partly paid with 25 stg pct payable onacceptance and the balance on July 1, 1987. REUTER&#3;